{
  "texts": [
    "The number of works providing a code repository is significantly smaller, at 113 (∼ 53%).",
    "This figure excludes papers that provided a link to a non-existent or empty repository.",
    "Overall, 72 (∼ 51%) of the pre-prints and 34 (∼ 48%) peer-reviewed papers provided both prompts and a repository.",
    "We report further details on this data in Appendix B.",
    "Another barrier to reproducibility is that most closed-source LLMs are being regularly updated."
  ]
}